{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2198","heading":"Report on territorial debt","label":"2198 Report on territorial debt","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/ch20/schIV","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Report required","label":"a Report required","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the historical levels of each territory’s public debt, current amount and composition of each territory’s public debt, and future projections of each territory’s public debt;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the historical levels of each territory’s revenue, current amount and composition of each territory’s revenue, and future projections of each territory’s revenue;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the drivers and composition of each territory’s public debt;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the effect of Federal laws, mandates, rules, and regulations on each territory’s public debt; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the ability of each territory to repay it’s public debt.1So in original. Probably should be “its”.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Materials","label":"b Materials","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2198","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft48%2Fs2198%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The government of each territory shall make available to the Comptroller General of the United States all materials necessary to carry out this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
